import "./order.css"; import Header from "../Components/Header/Header"; import Title from '../Components/Title/Title' import SummaryTable from './Components/Summary_table/table' import DetailTable from './Components/Detail_table/table' function Order(props) { return (
<div className="order-content"> <div className="order-detail"> <h2>Order Details</h2> <DetailTable /> </div> <div className="order-summary"> <h2>Order Summary</h2> <SummaryTable /> </div> <div className="my-feedback"> <h2>MY FEEDBACK</h2> <input type="number" min="0" max="5" id></input> </div> </div> </div> ); } export default Order;
